                <p>Gord is the Vice President of Technology at Primaris Management Inc., a leading Canadian mall owner and manager, and is the Chair of our Board of Advisors.  In his twenty-year IT career, he has extensive experience developing and executing technology strategies in a diverse range of business environments.  At Primaris, he oversees the company's business information, marketing and analytics systems, and is responsible for the development of its smart buildings strategy.  Prior to entering the real estate business, he held a senior technology role directing IT growth and innovation at one of Canada's premier public attractions.  Gord is a graduate of the University of Ottawa, and is a board member of the Realcomm real estate advisory council.</p>
